oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Homecoming Floats
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Homecomings; Floats (Parades); Ships
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A color image of the first prize-winning float for Christian Brothers' 1967 Homecoming. A giant Buccaneer can be seen in the background with Battersby Hall behind it.
